<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7651> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7651" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Quaestor ca. 74-66, termed a senator in 66 (Cic. Cluent. 165). See MRR 2.103. His coinage is dated to 74 by Crawford, RRC 1.408, no. 396. For a stemma, see Wiseman, NM 251, nos. 318 and 320.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4420> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4420" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Grueber (CRRBM 1.404f.) dates him in 74, Sobeck (48) before 66, when Cicero refers to him as a senator (Cluent. 165). Dated ca. 72 by Sydenham (Ixiii)." .
